An Amisom military vehicle on Thursday hit and injured popular Somali Musician Jimi Sheikh Mumin before speeding away from the accident scene. The 77 yr old Musician was rushed to Medina Hospital after sustaining injuries in the accident.Mumin was a member of the Waberi Music group which was made up of popular Somali musicians of the 80s. AMISOM has lately been on the focus following accidents involving it's vehicles and civilians where in some instances have been fatal.